- Fixed `admin-web/src/app/(admin)/orders/page.tsx` — Added `mapOrder()` mapping function, `deriveStatus()` for consolidated order status, `payMethodMap` for payment method display. Fixed API parameters and removed mock data fallback.
- Fixed `admin-web/src/app/(admin)/experts/page.tsx` — Added `mapApiItemToExpert()` for `specialties` → `specialty`, `introduction` → `intro`, `created_at` → `createdAt`. Form submission also maps correctly.
- Fixed `admin-web/src/app/(admin)/content/articles/page.tsx` — Added `mapArticleFromApi()` for `view_count` → `views`, `like_count` → `likes`, `author_id` → `authorId`, `created_at` → `createdAt`.
- Fixed `admin-web/src/app/(admin)/content/videos/page.tsx` — Added `mapVideoFromApi()` for `video_url` → `videoUrl`, `cover_image` → `coverUrl`, `view_count` → `views`, `like_count` → `likes`.
- Fixed `admin-web/src/app/(admin)/services/items/page.tsx` — Added `mapServiceItemFromApi()` for `category_id` → `categoryId`, `original_price` → `originalPrice`, `sales_count` → `sales`.
- Fixed `admin-web/src/app/(admin)/points/mall/page.tsx` — Added `mapMallItemFromApi()` for `type` → `category`, `price_points` → `points`, image extraction from `images` array.

### Verification

All 9 admin API endpoints return HTTP 200 with correct data structure. Admin frontend loads and renders data correctly for all menu pages.

