## Notes For Next Iteration

- Merchant identities are granted by admin only; new self-registered accounts still default to normal users.
- Old user and merchant accounts require admin-side manual merge before official cutover.
- If remote DB schema lags behind models, check startup schema synchronization and the new merchant-related tables first.
- SMS config can be managed from admin panel (系统管理 → 短信管理). Supports dual provider (Tencent Cloud + Alibaba Cloud), only one active at a time. DB config takes priority over env vars.
- To enable real SMS sending: configure via admin panel (dual provider supported) or set `TENCENT_SMS_SECRET_ID` and `TENCENT_SMS_SECRET_KEY` environment variables.
- WeChat push config: 系统管理 → 微信推送管理. Email notify config: 系统管理 → 邮件通知管理 (with logs and test send).
- The old `POST /api/admin/settings/push` endpoint is deprecated (returns 410 Gone). Use the new independent module APIs instead.
